ServerRequest

public ServerRequest(AbstractBindingBase b,
                     ObjectMessageContext objectContext)
Used to create a ServerRequest to represent a resent outgoing message. Hence the state is set up to allow us to proceed directly to the processOutbound() phase.

Parameters:
b - the underlying binding
objectContext - the object message context
